    "name": "Speed Creators",
    "steam_appid": 1745860,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/baccde15712e18a0839a01b0c4a551c8.poster.avif?t=1768361387\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/baccde15712e18a0839a01b0c4a551c8.webm?t=1768361387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/baccde15712e18a0839a01b0c4a551c8.mp4?t=1768361387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against your friends in one massive sprawling level created by you and your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First everyone is given a time limit to create and beat a small level.  Then all levels that make it through are stitched together with checkpoints along the way.  Then run for glory as you watch your friends slowly go insane trying to beat your level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use traps and blocks with special properties to make your level however you want, whether that's tough as nails platforming or a satisfying parkour challenge.  How the final level turns out is entirely up to the nature of the players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/05e96c88718c45d0ce89bfcbd631f3b1.poster.avif?t=1768361387\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/05e96c88718c45d0ce89bfcbd631f3b1.webm?t=1768361387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/05e96c88718c45d0ce89bfcbd631f3b1.mp4?t=1768361387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cool Features-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer for anywhere from 2-200 players</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dozens of unique traps and blocks with different effects and utilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A special bond with your level that results in a one of a kind feeling as you watch your friends slowly lose their minds on your own creation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw tomatoes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple but precise platforming</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Punch your friends</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modifiers that let you control how the game is played</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precise and responsive movement</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create, play, and share custom levels online  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hats, lots of hats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/e522568f1c88a4d8f1ec754bfae1f2dd.poster.avif?t=1768361387\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/e522568f1c88a4d8f1ec754bfae1f2dd.webm?t=1768361387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745860/extras/e522568f1c88a4d8f1ec754bfae1f2dd.mp4?t=1768361387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed Creators is meant to be played online with friends.  However you can create levels offline in a solo level editor and share them online.</p>",
